db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23495, line : "25 It is, indeed not easy to calculate the height to which the memory"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23496, line : "may be cultivated. To take an ordinary case, we might refer to that"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23497, line : "of any first rate actor, who must be prepared, at a very short"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23498, line : "warning, to 'rhapsodize,' night after night, parts which when laid"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23499, line : "together, would amount to an immense number of lines. But all this"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23500, line : "is nothing to two instances of our own day. Visiting at Naples a"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23501, line : "gentleman of the highest intellectual attainments, and who held a"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23502, line : "distinguished rank among the men of letters in the last century, he"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23503, line : "informed us that the day before he had passed much time in examining"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23504, line : "a man, not highly educated, who had learned to repeat the whole"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23505, line : "Gierusalemme of Tasso, not only to recite it consecutively, but also"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23506, line : "to repeat those stanzas in utter defiance of the sense, either"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23507, line : "forwards or backwards, or from the eighth line to the first,"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23508, line : "alternately the odd and even lines--in short, whatever the passage"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23509, line : "required; the memory, which seemed to cling to the words much more"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23510, line : "than to the sense, had it at such perfect command, that it could"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23511, line : "produce it under any form. Our informant went on to state that this"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23512, line : "singular being was proceeding to learn the Orlando Furioso in the"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23513, line : "same manner. But even this instance is less wonderful than one as to"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23514, line : "which we may appeal to any of our readers that happened some twenty"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23515, line : "years ago to visit the town of Stirling, in Scotland. No such person"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23516, line : "can have forgotten the poor, uneducated man Blind Jamie who could"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23517, line : "actually repeat, after a few minutes consideration any verse"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23518, line : "required from any part of the Bible--even the obscurest and most"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23519, line : "unimportant enumeration of mere proper names not excepted. We do not"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23520, line : "mention these facts as touching the more difficult part of the"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23521, line : "question before us, but facts they are; and if we find so much"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23522, line : "difficulty in calculating the extent to which the mere memory may be"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23523, line : "cultivated, are we, in these days of multifarious reading, and of"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23524, line : "countless distracting affairs, fair judges of the perfection to"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23525, line : "which the invention and the memory combined may attain in a simpler"});
db.iliad.insert({ pg : 23526, line : "age, and among a more single minded people?--Quarterly Review, _l."});
